些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=wjS%2BXIWiU%2Bk%2BaZlvRNiLW7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6e9f5c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"9f206dda97257d422f51e034aa6cb985d0623e89","tid":908560,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點都好 屋企人先會永遠支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b867902d753cbe07182cec1a3bc0a78cd447694c","tid":908560,"uid":202409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auNpPvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauNpPvf.jpg&h=e8eeb626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0def9f0244b044ca9a8eeb553b9cfe3fc37e4db1","tid":908560,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"人生總有低潮 慢慢等佢過就好了"},{"pid":"768678c030f8c58907d3fe500e868866c0231122","tid":908560,"uid":89892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c189456f56d9624bfae22a15e2f6f19ba37fe4f3","tid":908560,"uid":143040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"Fresh grad 返咗三個月工而家又失業，畢業之前又俾ex 拋棄，愛情事業雙失，好似個廢青<img src=\"/asset